a simple form service

1. build

  $ make build

2. create a config json file

  {
    "title": "My Survey",
    "fields": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "prompt": "What's your name?"
      },
      {
        "type": "select",
        "prompt": "What's your favorite pokemon?"
        "options": [
          "Pikachu",
          "Ganger",
          "Exeggutor"
        ]
      }
    ]
  }

  check out example.json for full example or type defs in formo.ts

3. start the server

  $ ./build/formo myform.json

4. data will be saved to data.sqlite (or specified otherwise in config json)
